  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > SAVE EDMOND</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/423b53c51a59ba673127434e9aa8172b.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/423b53c51a59ba673127434e9aa8172b.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/423b53c51a59ba673127434e9aa8172b.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Edmond is a lost fifty-year-old who missed his life. And on top of that, before ending his life, he forgot to set up an automatic reply on his mailbox. Unacceptable. Fortunately for him, <strong>and for you because otherwise there would be no game</strong>, Kairos will send him back to his past to change his destiny!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > WIN POGNON</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/9333a943c6e0d2d2a080d93624625f69.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/9333a943c6e0d2d2a080d93624625f69.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/9333a943c6e0d2d2a080d93624625f69.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cross the street and find a passion job that doesn't pay in visibility in order to gain access to high-end vehicles, a suit, and eventually a castle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > DEVELOP THE CITY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fc56fd23cded47b8e92363137cd93b9c.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fc56fd23cded47b8e92363137cd93b9c.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fc56fd23cded47b8e92363137cd93b9c.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Edit the city because it's your PROJEEEET and you're going to make it WIN.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > RELEASE YOUR SKILLS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/5d6a1c1991222625373bff56f6391af4.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/5d6a1c1991222625373bff56f6391af4.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/5d6a1c1991222625373bff56f6391af4.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unleash your #skills to #growth your #efficiency. #personaldevelopment<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > BREAKING DOWN SLICES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fe0a3bb7074d8b6ab99469d6fe1991d1.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fe0a3bb7074d8b6ab99469d6fe1991d1.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/fe0a3bb7074d8b6ab99469d6fe1991d1.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Because why not.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > MEET YOUR NEIGHBORS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/cae66ab89bf0cbc81365cff5f27d089d.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/cae66ab89bf0cbc81365cff5f27d089d.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/cae66ab89bf0cbc81365cff5f27d089d.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Meet Jamil the manly country boy with refined facial capillarity, Simon the LifeStyle influencer or Godefroy who will help you assert your social positioning.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > MAKE TIPS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/6dd035f3d902d553e8b507e42695b62f.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/6dd035f3d902d553e8b507e42695b62f.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/6dd035f3d902d553e8b507e42695b62f.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rummage through the garbage, collect 5 stones, 6 screws and 2 boards to make a whole series of furniture in one click (because it's a simulation, but it's mostly a video game first!).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPUSHES THE EXTRATERRENT QUENILS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/098707cf95fda84c8abc1f1069b70d6d.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/098707cf95fda84c8abc1f1069b70d6d.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/098707cf95fda84c8abc1f1069b70d6d.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Because always why not.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ALTERNATIVE ENDINGS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/82e311f4cb07919977d394d125ffb7a8.poster.avif?t=1718488826\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/82e311f4cb07919977d394d125ffb7a8.webm?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/82e311f4cb07919977d394d125ffb7a8.mp4?t=1718488826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Edmond guide for (non-exhaustive possibilities):<br>- Let him destroy capitalism<br>- Go to Mars and become Edmond Musk<br>- Let him be eaten by a dinosaur<br>- ...<br><br><strong>In short Kairos'Light is : </strong><br>Projeeeets, inhabitants with particular whims, business that works at the moment and the energies of the cosmic Christ that makes cabins grow in the trees.<br>Kairos'Light, because why not.<br>A crazy and free adventure.",
